org.neuroph.contrib.neat.gen.operations
Interface OrganismSelector

All Known Implementing Classes:
NaturalSelectionOrganismSelector
public interface OrganismSelector

An OrganismSelector is responsible for determining which Organisms to keep after a generation step. Simple implementations will consider issues such as roulette wheel selection and elitism.

Author:
Aidan Morgan
